    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story So Far.......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/8740c7669bc5fd0e95e018771f4cc98d.avif?t=1769465497\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras_big/8740c7669bc5fd0e95e018771f4cc98d.avif?t=1769465497 width=800 height=896 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyberpunk Zombie Shooter:</strong> Immerse yourself in a dark, futuristic world overrun by deadly Zombots.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7eef2bc85cb1d67b14bece9b94b60eee.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7eef2bc85cb1d67b14bece9b94b60eee.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7eef2bc85cb1d67b14bece9b94b60eee.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Six City Zones:</strong> Battle through six unique city zones, each under siege and guarded by menacing bosses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/2f2b52a8671faaca2d75e2e5a65d37c0.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/2f2b52a8671faaca2d75e2e5a65d37c0.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/2f2b52a8671faaca2d75e2e5a65d37c0.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Combat: Face off against Zombots and enemies with a variety of weapons and special ammo.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/f94e5405dfc49fc893e3742793f408ea.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/f94e5405dfc49fc893e3742793f408ea.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/f94e5405dfc49fc893e3742793f408ea.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single-Player or Co-Op Play:</strong> Tackle missions solo or team up with friends to take on the Zombot hordes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/78eb39cd05808817511e98732cd31af7.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/78eb39cd05808817511e98732cd31af7.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/78eb39cd05808817511e98732cd31af7.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Boss Fights:</strong> Face off against formidable bosses that test your skill and strategy in each zone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/22170458f65e36d36a6f03eccf211b36.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/22170458f65e36d36a6f03eccf211b36.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/22170458f65e36d36a6f03eccf211b36.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Environments:</strong> Navigate through diverse, futuristic landscapes, each offering its own set of challenges and surprises.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7d88e792b265de96089f31fc3a87f56a.poster.avif?t=1769465497\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7d88e792b265de96089f31fc3a87f56a.webm?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074330/extras/7d88e792b265de96089f31fc3a87f56a.mp4?t=1769465497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
